body: This file is automatically generated (using `protoc`) from [`error_codes.proto`](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/lib/core/error_codes.proto). If you build TensorFlow using Bazel, the file will be generated for you. Otherwise, you will need to run `protoc` on that file to generate the C++ implementation of that type (and the other protocol buffers that TensorFlow uses).
